illiam|last=Bryan|date=4 June 2018|publisher=}}</ref> |- | Wright, Gillian | [[James Webb Space Telescope|JWST]]/MIRI | PI (Eur)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://jwst.nasa.gov/meet-wright.html|title=The James Webb Space Telescope|website=jwst.nasa.gov}}</ref> |- | Wright, Shelley | [[Thirty Meter Telescope|TMT]]/IRIS | PS<ref>{{cite web|url=https://irlab.astro.ucla.edu/iris/|title=IRIS Home Page|website=irlab.astro.ucla.edu}}</ref> |- | [[Maria Zuber|Zuber, Maria]] | GRAIL | PI<ref>{{cite web|url=http://moon.mit.edu/|title=GRAIL - Gravity Recovery and Interior Laboratory|website=moon.mit.edu}}</ref> |}
